  20,40,Tuus soror walked them dictus ‘ego tell vos nursing mater take bonus care de eum. ' Nos sic returned vos tuus mater ut she est happy stop injuria Ac when vos killed person nos saved vos grievous consequences; indeed nos tested vos thoroughly. Vos stayed annus people Midyan statim vos advenit prout precise plan
